				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-649550#post-1773612</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-649550/scp-1817#post-1773612</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2013 18:07:33 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>wishun</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1204404</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Demonic(?) organization parallel to the Foundation, what's not to love?</p> <p>The containment procedures should have some contingency for when/if the big, bad REDACTED get out again. Yes, the mist monsters with the grab-bag anatomy seem to be doing a pretty good job so far; but the Foundation are the sort of people who wear a belt, suspenders, and carry a spare pair of each just in case.</p> <p>While I'm thinking on the REDACTEDs; it works pretty well as a plot device but I can't think of a single in-universe reason for that censoring. On the contrary, it would be important information for anyone working on or near this area. You need to have at least some idea of what's coming if all hell breaks loose.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
